    <title>Consumer-Driven Class Pricing</title>
    <updated>2026-03-12T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Zuhui Xiao</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;b&gt;Marketing Science&lt;/b&gt; &lt;br&gt;This paper proposes a consumer loss aversion-based rationale for class pricing, which is the practice of assigning only a few price points to many differentiated products.</content>
